{
  "stem": "107.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a central hospital, not anymore belonging to any of these Jewish camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he made a left turn, opened the gate and said, go in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If it would have been further, we would have gone to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They wouldn't have opened the gas for four or five people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE] it had single people there-- with-- put [? some rooms in ?] wall, [? and shoot us. ?] Again we were saved for the moment.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The head of this camp was a Polish physician, a prisoner, but a privileged man-- a Polish military physician-- a great anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were [? really no ?] Jews there in this camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he said we have order to occupy you in our medical work here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so we were alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In this night, the whole Czech camp was [NON-ENGLISH] emptied out on trucks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night we heard the trucks going to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Next morning the camp was empty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Smoke was all that remained.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There were my parents, Willie Shoenfeld, all our patients-- this time seven.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean we had fought to keep some people alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was the end --and many others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I mean, there is no qualification who should or should not, or what it means.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "To me it meant, of course, tragedy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because there I had lost my parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I stayed in this camp for a few more months [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when I heard that a transport from Holland [INAUDIBLE] arrived.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And my fear was, of course, that my sister could be on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now I had met a Slovakian doctor in this central camp whose wife had a kind of position in the female camp, in the woman's camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
